Bini Smaghi Says ECB Ready to Do What’s Needed on Liquidity

-- B y   T i m o t h y   H o m a n
-- 
2011-09-26T14:24:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/bini-smaghi-says-ecb-ready-to-do-what-s-needed-on-liquidity.html
European Central Bank Executive
Board member Lorenzo  Bini Smaghi  said the ECB will do whatever
is necessary to supply sufficient funds to European banks.  “For liquidity, we are there” and “we are ready to do
what is needed,” Bini Smaghi said in  New York  today. “"We need
to reassure the markets.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
